443
00:37:42,956 --> 00:37:44,566
All right, um...

444
00:37:47,482 --> 00:37:49,658
The police, they, um...

445
00:37:49,832 --> 00:37:51,617
They came to gym class today.

446
00:37:52,574 --> 00:37:53,880
