stupid kid's thing.

451
00:38:13,334 --> 00:38:14,466
JAMES: What is it?

452
00:38:16,337 --> 00:38:17,338
DAVARA: I don't know.

453
00:38:17,512 --> 00:38:19,862
Some story started
going around

454
00:38:20,036 --> 00:38:22,474
