the old Chain of Rocks Bridge.

463
00:38:50,066 --> 00:38:52,155
You know where that is?

464
00:38:52,417 --> 00:38:53,461
JAMES: Yeah. Yeah, I know.

465
00:38:54,941 --> 00:38:57,726
AMANDA: When I was little,
I had this theory

466
